* ðŸ”‘ JWT = stateless authentication No need to store user sessions on the server; JWT contains all necessary data.
* Process overview
 ----(A) Signup
    User registers âž” password is hashed âž” saved in DB âž” JWT is generated âž” sent to user.
 ----(B) Login
    User submits email/password âž” server verifies âž” generates JWT âž” sends to user.
 ----(C) Protected route
    User sends request with JWT âž” server verifies token âž” allows access.

